subject: Repository layout adjusted and manifest added
commitMessage:
Repository layout adjusted and manifest added

- files moved from eail dir to 'root'
- manifest added and spec adjusted
- removed conditional checks of glib version, allowing
  to install package on emulator 3.0 images.
- removed RPMLint warnings
- unhardcode path to elm modules
- fixed pkgconfig_requires_private in pc file
- create symlink instead of copying lib to elm moculdes
- README and changelog updated

Change-Id: I3c4d683772c58cfd0fafa4142b92e6343bcc602a
